                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>Hey {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},
&lt;p&gt;Your gene test has officially shipped! Generally, it takes 2-4 business days to arrive, but depending on the postal service, give or take a day.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Make sure to check your mail- you&amp;rsquo;ll want to take your test as soon as you can. It&amp;rsquo;s important we get a fast turnaround time so we can analyze and deliver your results ASAP.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;u&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s what to do next:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;STEP 1&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Watch this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.10xyourhealth.com/genetickit-instructions&quot;&gt;video&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;on how to take your test. It&amp;rsquo;s a very easy process and there are also instructions in the package itself, but we wanted to provide this to you in case you wanted to watch it beforehand.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;STEP 2&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ship your test back to us ASAP and we&amp;rsquo;ll take it from there! Results typically take 12-15 business days to process, and we&amp;#39;ll let you know the moment your results are ready!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s that simple. Once you do that, a totally customized genetic test report will be generated for you that offers a full, comprehensive snapshot of your current state of wellness&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;AND&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;what you can do to supplement your gene function in areas where you might be deficient.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can track your shipment by clicking on this link:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;{{{Opportunity.First_Tracking_URL__c}}}&quot;&gt;{{{Opportunity.First_Tracking_URL__c}}}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions, please let us know. We are here for you every step of the way!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To your wellness,&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;10&lt;span style=&quot;color:#c0392b;&quot;&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Health Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Main: 305.682.1818&lt;br /&gt;
Fax: 786.598.8612&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://10xhealthsystem.com&quot;&gt;10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
